{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't yet nothing organized or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in this way, we also let know Piotr to tell my brothers that we are not anymore in the ghetto of Glebokie, but we went to Postawy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because my brothers thought by any kind of-- maybe they could come to the ghetto there, because it was closer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they could maybe take us all out to the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they would arrange that we should be in the woods for all of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We stayed in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my uncles gave us-- by the way, the-- in the ghetto, the houses of my uncles' were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we had space where we can sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they had, at that time, still quite a bit of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we weren't hungry anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We stayed there for several months, until late fall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they decided to liquidate this ghetto, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] This time, they were more thorough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had machine guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were really organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We start, again, running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't let my mother out of my hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGHS] It was very, very cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we start running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the people start falling, falling, falling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was-- they were shooting with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was without stopping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was back and forth, like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they were-- people were falling so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was running with my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She got shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] And I stood over her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SOBBING] She start begging me [CRYING] and promise me that I would run.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
